%% MyAIStorybook - System Sequence Diagram: Character Chat Scenario

sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant System as :System
    
    Note over User,System: Character Chat Scenario (Main Success)<br/>System is treated as BLACK BOX
    
    User->>System: selectStory(story_id)
    System-->>User: story_details
    
    User->>System: selectCharacter(character_name)
    System-->>User: chat_ready
    
    loop conversation continues
        User->>System: sendMessage(message_text)
        System-->>User: character_response(response_text)
    end
    
    User->>System: endChat()
    System-->>User: chat_ended
    
    Note right of System: System operations are high-level<br/>Character responses generated internally<br/>Focus on WHAT system does
